com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit

Class Place

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit.Place
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Place
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The Place class represents a single Place created within your Kit.

    A Place may be a Geofence or a Beacon, and is used as a geographic marker to trigger an associated Campaign.

    Places are also used to mark a location where a Campaign was found. This provides richer data to be saved within Campaign Kit's analytics.
    See Also:
    CampaignKitNotifier.didDetectPlace(Place, com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit.CampaignKitNotifier.CKEventType), Campaign.saveAnalyticRecord(com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit.CampaignKitNotifier.CKAnalyticsType, Place), Serialized Form
